## Fast gate (run after every task)

**Concurrent agents (default — use this):**
```bash
# Lint only touched paths — ~5s
pnpm exec eslint --max-warnings=0 <path1> [path2 ...]

# Incremental typecheck — ~10s warm
pnpm typecheck
```

**Solo agent only:**
```bash
pnpm typecheck
pnpm lint
```

Both forms must exit 0. No exceptions. This is the non-negotiable close condition.
Full decision table: `.cursor/rules/targeted-verification.mdc`.

---

## Pre-push gate (run before opening a PR — ~3 min)

```bash
pnpm verify:parallel
```

This includes knip, format check, all typechecks, and behavior tests. Run it once before pushing, not after every file edit.

---

## Shell migration specifics

After any Workbench/Nexus phase work:

- `organizationAppsPath(slug, "home")` resolves to Nexus root `/o/${slug}`.
- `switchActiveOrgAction` redirect goes to `/o/${slug}`, not `/o/${slug}/dashboard`.
- Shell chrome is **`components2/app-shell/`** (`#app-shell`). `components2/nexus/` = Nexus Field + Lynx summon only. No repo-root `components/` or `components/dashboard/`.

```powershell
# Phantom typecheck errors after a route deletion? Clear Next.js type cache:
Remove-Item -Recurse -Force .next\types -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue
Remove-Item -Recurse -Force .next\dev -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue
pnpm typecheck
```

---

## Close condition

```txt
Task is closed only when:
  pnpm exec eslint --max-warnings=0 <touched-paths> → exits 0   (concurrent agents)
  OR pnpm lint → exits 0                                          (solo agent)
  pnpm typecheck → exits 0
  No import targets a file that does not exist on disk
  No redirect targets a deleted route
  All stale "Phase N" comments are resolved or renamed to a future phase
```
